	<p>TOWIE star Lauren Pope has revealed that she has the PIP breast implants that have been at the <a href="http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/top-stories/2012/01/09/cosmetic-surgery-firm-transform-refuse-free-removal-of-pip-breast-implants-115875-23691563/">centre of a health scare</a> for the last few weeks. Lauren - who was formerly a glamour model - talks about her concern over the implants in the Tonight show, which is on tomorrow evening.</p>&#13;
